parallel.distributed

Class DAccMsg

  • java.lang.Object
    • parallel.distributed.DAccMsg
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DAccNumberRequest, DAccNumbersRequest, DAccSerDblPairRequest, DGetArgMaxObjectRequest, DGetArgMinObjectRequest, DGetMaxNumberRequest, DGetMinNumberRequest, DGetSumOfNumbersRequest, DShutDownSrvRequest

    public abstract class DAccMsg
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    DAccMsg objects are meant to transport over Socket wires number accumulation requests (accumulate-data or get[Min/Max/Sum...] requests). Not part of the public API (despite the public status).
